{"tid":2090934,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE將登NHK 9人齊露腿根...子瑜長腿驚人","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T09:24:59.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"991161255076f0da140ed5d9b63d7c9907575bd8","tid":2090934,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"南韓大勢女團TWICE，積極發展日本市場，8日將正式發行第6張日文單曲〈Fanfare〉，上月19號官方先推出MV和音源，就登上日本LINE MUSIC冠軍，這禮拜六(4日)她們更會出演NHK深夜音樂節目《涉谷之聲》，近日，NHK先釋出預告，9位成員一字排開齊露長腿，台灣成員周子瑜身材更是高挑，令人驚豔。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員全穿上白色單品，9人一字排開齊露長腿，而身材最高挑的子瑜，也高出成員半個頭以上，令人驚艷不已，粉絲看了都直呼「九妞妞全穿短的實在太惹火」、「怎麼這麼可愛，受不了啦」。<br />\n<br />\n其實，子瑜剛出道時官方身高是169公分，但隨著她不斷長高，明顯比成員高出半個頭，有傳她已經172公分，不過她上個月生日開直播時，親自回應「我170公分」，但有些心虛表示「應該是啦」。"},{"pid":"ff38082fba74a77c28ed6f77d1b3a6750808f42a","tid":2090934,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-07-02/900/20200702003685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-07-02%2F900%2F20200702003685.jpg&h=7133082a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE週六將上NHK深夜音樂節目《涉谷之聲》。(圖／翻攝自TWICE JAPAN推特)"},{"pid":"3591938ca2ca9d83682531307d50765999ec652f","tid":2090934,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc49235e70dc039ca08dc7b894ce8323f418023","tid":2090934,"uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3591938ca2ca9d83682531307d50765999ec652f","tid":2090934,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c